941
01:06:11,393 --> 01:06:12,936
No.

942
01:06:13,019 --> 01:06:14,770
Yeah!

943
01:06:16,188 --> 01:06:18,023
All right. OK.

944
01:06:24,155 --> 01:06:25,531
Ten minutes, love.

945
01:06:25,614 --> 01:06:26,699
Thank you.

946
01:06:26,782 --> 01:06:28,533
Man says he loves me.

947
01:06:28,616 --> 01:06:31,619
